---
title: Honey Chantenay Carrots and Miso Aubergine with Bulgur, Roasted Beetroot and Fresh Pomegranate
description: We love good Miso Auberine & Beetroot Bulgur Salad and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-chantenay-carrots-miso-auberine-27383d5d-c5c862ae.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/honey-chantenay-carrots-miso-auberine-5f63345604af642f75674468-7fe07f5c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/honey-chantenay-carrots-miso-auberine-5f63345604af642f75674468
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Fusion
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 440 kcal
  fat: 6 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
  carbohydrates: 79 g
  sugar: 29 g
  protein: 15 g
  sodium: 1.7 g
  serving size: 517
